\", \"from\": 737, \"to\": 739}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Martin, a three-time Olympian, had been working with Goodwin up until the time of her death when she reached the height of her success in eventing, a competitive equestrian event that includes dressage, cross country and show jumping.\", \"from\": 760, \"to\": 994, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 760, \"end\": 766, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martin_Crane\", \"score\": 0.9999999953956831, \"rank\": 4.603234456324358e-09, \"text\": \"Martin\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martin_Crane\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martin_Crane\"}, {\"begin\": 781, \"end\": 789, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999949556458786, \"rank\": 5.0443795995192335e-06, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 922, \"end\": 932, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrian_at_the_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.90468812116032, \"rank\": 0.10535329978392824, \"text\": \"equestrian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrian_at_the_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrian_at_the_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Goodwin\", \"from\": 813, \"to\": 820}, {\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 830, \"to\": 838}, {\"ngram\": \"her death\", \"from\": 842, \"to\": 851}, {\"ngram\": \"the height\", \"from\": 869, \"to\": 879}, {\"ngram\": \"her success\", \"from\": 883, \"to\": 894}, {\"ngram\": \"dressage\", \"from\": 953, \"to\": 961}, {\"ngram\": \"cross country\", \"from\": 963, \"to\": 976}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Just a few months before her death, Goodwin rode Bruno to a sixth-place finish at the Prestigious Land Rover Kentucky Three-Day Event.\", \"from\": 995, \"to\": 1129, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her