d a miscalculation at a jump and, unfortunately, Bruno got his legs tangled up and absolutely cartwheeled and, sadly, killed Annie.\", \"from\": 1329, \"to\": 1498, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1330, \"end\": 1335, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Annie_Brackett\", \"score\": 0.9563695548087203, \"rank\": 0.04559478593592849, \"text\": \"Annie\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Annie_Brackett\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Annie_Brackett\"}, {\"begin\": 1492, \"end\": 1497, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Annie_Brackett\", \"score\": 0.9563695548087203, \"rank\": 0.04559478593592849, \"text\": \"Annie\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Annie_Brackett\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Annie_Brackett\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Bruno\", \"from\": 1349, \"to\": 1354}, {\"ngram\": \"a miscalculation\", \"from\": 1369, \"to\": 1385}, {\"ngram\": \"a jump\", \"from\": 1389, \"to\": 1395}, {\"ngram\": \"Bruno\", \"from\": 1416, \"to\": 1421}, {\"ngram\": \"his legs\", \"from\": 1426, \"to\": 1434}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And, you know, it was just a surreal moment.\", \"from\": 1499, \"to\": 1543, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"just a surreal moment\", \"from\": 1521, \"to\": 1542}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We were just all in disbelief that something like that would have happened,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1545, \"to\": 1631, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"disbelief\", \"from\": 1566, \"to\": 1575}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1581, \"to\": 1590}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And on top of that, it was like Annie was a great rider and this is a great jumper, you know?\", \"from\": 1632, \"to\": 1726, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1665, \"end\": 1670, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Annie_Brackett\", \"score\": 0.9563695548087203, \"rank\": 0.04559478593592849, \"text\": \"Annie\", \