964}, {\"ngram\": \"the cattle\", \"from\": 1982, \"to\": 1992}, {\"ngram\": \"a polo player\", \"from\": 2001, \"to\": 2014}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her mother trained racehorses and was an eventer.\", \"from\": 2016, \"to\": 2065, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her mother\", \"from\": 2016, \"to\": 2026}, {\"ngram\": \"racehorses\", \"from\": 2035, \"to\": 2045}, {\"ngram\": \"an eventer\", \"from\": 2054, \"to\": 2064}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So it was just a natural transition, I guess, for Annie to fall into that,\\\" her father, Putter Goodwin, said.\", \"from\": 2067, \"to\": 2177, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2118, \"end\": 2123, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Annie_Brackett\", \"score\": 0.9563695548087203, \"rank\": 0.04559478593592849, \"text\": \"Annie\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Annie_Brackett\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Annie_Brackett\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"just a natural transition\", \"from\": 2078, \"to\": 2103}, {\"ngram\": \"her father\", \"from\": 2144, \"to\": 2154}, {\"ngram\": \"Putter Goodwin\", \"from\": 2156, \"to\": 2170}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She just always loved them from day one.\\\"\", \"from\": 2178, \"to\": 2220, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"day\", \"from\": 2211, \"to\": 2214}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That love continued to grow through college when Goodwin decided she wanted to pursue eventing.\", \"from\": 2222, \"to\": 2317, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"That love\", \"from\": 2222, \"to\": 2231}, {\"ngram\": \"college\", \"from\": 2258, \"to\": 2265}, {\"ngram\": \"Goodwin\", \"from\": 2271, \"to\": 2278}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She soon discovered Bruno, whose competition name is Fedarman B, and purchased and imported him from Europe.\", \"from\": 2318, \"to\": 2426, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Bruno\", \"from\": 2338, \"to\": 2343}, {\"ngram\": \"whose competition name\", \"from\": 2345, \"to\": 2367}, {\"ngram\": \"Fedarman B\", \"from\": 2371, \"to\": 2381}, {\"ngram\": \"Europe\", \"from\": 2419, \"to\": 2425}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She literally found him on the internet and sent me video of him just free jumping,\\\" Putter Goodwin said.\", \"from\": 2428, \"to\": 2534, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the internet\", \"from\": 2456, \"to\": 2468}, {\"ngram\": \"video\", \"from\": 2481, \"to\": 2486}, {\"ngram\": \"just free jumping\", \"from\": 2494, \"to\": 2511}, {\"ngram\": \"Putter Goodwin\", \"from\": 2514, \"to\": 2528}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And I mean, he just had such an incredibly natural jump ... just remember her saying, 'Dad, I think this is the one!'\\\"\", \"from\": 2535, \"to\": 2654, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"such an incredibly natural jump\", \"from\": 2560, \"to\": 2591}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Goodwin became a full-time professional rider and trainer and opened her own boarding facility on a farm in South Carolina.\", \"from\": 2658, \"to\": 2781, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2766, \"end\": 2780, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Carolina\", \"score\": 0.9925867235052264, \"rank\": 0.007467286312780616, \"text\": \"South Carolina\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Carolina\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Carolina\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Goodwin\", \"from\": 2658, \"to\": 2665}, {\"ngram\": \"a full-time professional rider\", \"from\": 2673, \"to\": 2703}, {\"ngram\": \"trainer\", \"from\": 2708, \"to\": 2715}, {\"ngram\": \"her own boarding facility\", \"from\": 2727, \"to\": 2752}, {\"ngram\": \"a farm\", \"from\": 2756, \"to\": 2762}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her belief in Bruno continued to grow as the chemistry and bond between the two further developed.\", \"from\": 2782, \"to\": 2880, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her belief\", \"from\": 2782, \"to\": 2792}, {\"ngram\": \"Bruno\", \"from\": 2796, \"to\": 2801}, {\"ngram\": \"the chemistry\", \"from\": 2823, \"to\": 2836}, {\"ngram\": \"bond\", \"from\": 2841, \"to\": 2845}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She was a real believer in this horse,\\\" Martin said.\", \"from\": 2882, \"to\": 2935, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2923, \"end\": 2929, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martin_Crane\", \"score\": 0.9999999953956831, \"rank\": 4.603234456324358e-09, \"text\": \"Martin\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martin_Crane\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martin_Crane\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a real believer\", \"from\": 2891, \"to\": 2906}, {\"ngram\": \"this horse\", \"from\": 2910, \"to\": 2920}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And do not forget, she did all the work here.\", \"from\": 2936, \"to\": 2982, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all the work\", \"from\": 2964, \"to\": 2976}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Like, she brought him on as a 3-year-old.\", \"from\": 2983, \"to\": 3024, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She imported him.\", \"from\": 3025, \"to\": 3042, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She taught him how to jump.\", \"from\": 3043, \"to\": 3070, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She took him to the first baby competitions, and she sort of got him up to the the top level of the sport.\", \"from\": 3071, \"to\": 3177, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the first baby competitions\", \"from\": 3087, \"to\": 3114}, {\"ngram\": \"the the top level\", \"from\": 3146, \"to\": 3163}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 3167, \"to\": 3176}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And, sometimes I feel a bit guilty, actually, you know.\", \"from\": 3178, \"to\": 3233, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Like, I am sort of here about to put my American team jacket on and compete at the biggest c